reviewText: Good performance, but the video is poorly shot and also not very sharp.

The DVD might have been good, but I found out that on playing it, the sound level was very low and was drowned out by the large amount of hiss.  Making the viewing experience bad.  Seems like an odd thing given todays technology.
Joe Louis Walker, master blues guitarist always comes to play, and never disappoints, this show is certainly no exception!
